ui.outputpanels

Class DataPanel

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.awt.Component
      • java.awt.Container
        • javax.swing.JComponent

  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.awt.image.ImageObserver, java.awt.MenuContainer, java.io.Serializable, javax.accessibility.Accessible

    public class DataPanel
extends OutputPanel
    DataPanel displays the internal ODE curve point data. The display consists of a split pane: on the left is a Java swing tree view of the stored ODEs and their curves / equilibrium points, and on the right is an Inspector panel, which displays the specific information about the selected node.
    Author:
    Clinic 10-11, modified from Clinic 08-09
